me ），看看有哪些文件变动了，再针对性的获取呢? 这样 JS 就不用每次都改新文件名了。</p>\n","last_modified":1642991117,"replies":23,"id":830203},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1628872984","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1628872984","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":34963,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1628872984","stars":4721,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":36118,"username":"coolair","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/coolair","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4fe/52ac/36118_mini.png?m=1642386161","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4fe/52ac/36118_normal.png?m=1642386161","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4fe/52ac/36118_large.png?m=1642386161","created":1363654688,"last_modified":1642386161},"last_reply_by":"deplivesb","last_touched":1642992373,"title":"分享一个 Mac 下的截图工具 Shottr","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/830172","created":1642985434,"deleted":0,"content":"目前免费，功能很强大，可以滚动截图、元素删除、添加标记、测距、放大、文本识别、颜色提取等，大家可以看看。\r\n\r\nhttps://shottr.cc/","content_rendered":"<p>目前免费，功能很强大，可以滚动截图、元素删除、添加标记、测距、放大、文本识别、颜色提取等，大家可以看看。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://shottr.cc/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://shottr.cc/</a></p>\n","last_modified":1642985589,"replies":21,"id":830172},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":47205,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png